title: Traditional Bone-in Wings Near Me
contents: A mobile app that will send you notifications whenever restaurants near by has bone-in wings on the menu.

title: The Ultimate Animal Quiz
contents: A web app that will give users 10 new unique questions each day and track their progress of their knowledge in various categories of animals in different climates, countries and species!

title: Power Washing
contents: A game for Windows and macOS where players power-wash graffiti, hog trailers/barns, decks, homes and so on.
